dialogue: *Autumn leaves flutter around, it's the first day of school*

name: Player
dialogue: Wow, it’s finally the first day of senior year. I can’t believe time has passed by so quickly.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Welcome everyone, to our first day of school.

name: Teacher
dialogue: So over the summer, I’m sure many of you forgot the basics to JavaScript and CSS.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Let’s have a quick review, and then I’ll assign you all a small project.
Sorry Teacher! Got caught up in the main office.

name: Teacher
dialogue: No problem. Take a seat wherever you want.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Anyways, everyone, please log into your accounts.
Ah good. I’m LI1 by the way.

name: Player
dialogue: By the way, I’ve never seen you around. Are you new?

name: LI1
dialogue: Oh yeah. I transferred here for my last year.

name: LI1
dialogue: I didn’t really like my old school. Didn’t suit me.

name: Player
dialogue: I see. Well, welcome to our school.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Okay, so now for a quick partner project….

name: LI1
dialogue: Oh wow. Looks like we’re together.

name: LI1
dialogue: HEY [name}. Wanna sit here or the back?

name: Player
dialogue: So I was thinking our project could be a video game.

name: LI1
dialogue: Wow we’ve been working for a while.

name: LI1
dialogue: Think it’s time to call it a day?

name: LI1
dialogue: Should we meet again tomorrow or through text?

name: LI1
dialogue: AH, it was alright I guess. One of my classes gave me a bit of trouble, but it is okay.

name: LI1
dialogue: Group projects stress me out! This kid I was working with was so frustrating.

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Aw, I hope I’m not stressing you out.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Who are they? I’ll teach them a lesson.

name: LI1
dialogue: Nah, it’s good. Let’s get to work.

name: LI1
dialogue: Y’know, we’ve been at this for a while. Want me to get you something to eat?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: How chivalrous of you. One coffee please.

name: LI1
dialogue: Here you go. One piping hot coffee.

name: Player
dialogue: Thank you so much! So, how did you get into coding?

name: LI1
dialogue: Ah, well. My mom is a computer engineer, so I kinda got into that as a kid. She always signed me up for bootcamps and whatnot haha. What about you?

name: Player
dialogue: Oh I just thought it’d be cool to learn about this kind of stuff. I’ve never really liked any type of technology but I really wanted to try something out.

name: LI1
dialogue: That’s really cool. Do you like it so far?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: You’ve definitely made it more enjoyable.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Eh, it’s okay. I’m glad we get to work together though.

name: LI1
dialogue: Haha thanks, I like working with you too! We should meet up the day after tomorrow to continue.

name: Player
dialogue: Hm.. so English is over, I have Calculus, and then Comp Sci… and then I’m free to go!
I’m LI2, I saw you in English and I was wondering if I could meet up with you some time? I really need help with the homework.

name: Player
dialogue: Yeah of course! I’m free right now if you need help?

name: LI2
dialogue: OH that’s perfect. Thank you so much!

name: Player
dialogue: This is just LI2, they just need help with English homework.

name: LI1
dialogue: Ah, sorry LI2. [Name] and I need to work with our project.

name: Player
dialogue: But I thought we weren't meeting up until later-

name: LI1
dialogue: No we should meet up now.

name: Player
dialogue: I'm sorry I can't, I promised LI2 I'd help them.

name: LI2
dialogue: Yeah, I'm really sorry. I really need help with this.

name: LI1
dialogue: Are you sure? What is this, Honors English? Shouldn't be that hard. I'm sure there's a brain in there somewhere.

name: LI2
dialogue: Dude, what the heck? Can you back off?

name: LI1
dialogue: Why don't you do so first? [Name] and I have an important project that we need to work on. They can't focus on your homeowork.

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Hey wait a minute. I did tell LI2, I can help and we weren't een supposed to meet until tomorrow. There's time before our due date. We'll continue tomorrow.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Hey LI1, relax. It's fine, we can work on it today. LI2, how about I give you my number so you can text me?

name: Chioce 1
dialogue: Hey wait a minute. I did tell LI2, I can help and we weren't een supposed to meet until tomorrow. There's time before our due date. We'll continue tomorrow.

name: Player
dialogue: I have no idea. Let’s get going?

name: LI2
dialogue: So I’m not too sure about this paper I’ve written so far.

name: Player
dialogue: Hm… the introduction is alright, but the rest of it is wordy and contains a lot of purple prose. You should get more to the point.

name: LI2
dialogue: Like this? Should I take this out?

name: LI2
dialogue: Alright, I’m getting the hang of this now.

name: Player
dialogue: You actually aren’t a bad writer, do you write in your free time?

name: LI2
dialogue: No, that’s really nice of you though. I do write comics when I’m free though, so maybe that’s why?

name: Player
dialogue: Wait really? You can draw? Are you producing these whole comics by yourself?

name: LI2
dialogue: Yeah, haha. I could show you some right now if you want.

name: Player
dialogue: Wow… this is really beautiful. You’re really talented.

name: Player
dialogue: This character looks really familiar. I feel like I’ve seen them before.

name: LI2
dialogue: Do they? Ah maybe, I just thought of them in my head.

name: Player
dialogue: (they look like LI1.... was I too harsh on them before?)

name: LI2
dialogue: Hey, what’s wrong? You look a little sad.

name: Player
dialogue: (Crap!) Oh it’s nothing! Should we get back to work?

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Hey LI1, relax. It’s fine, we can work on it today. LI2, how about I give you my number so you can text me?

name: LI1
dialogue: Want to go somewhere else besides the cafe today?

name: LI1
dialogue: We can work at my house. I live close and I can make you dinner.

name: Player
dialogue: Wow… your house is kind of big.

name: Player
dialogue: Jesus, it’s even bigger inside. What do your parents do for a living?

name: LI1
dialogue: My mom is a lawyer and my dad is the CEO of some big company. They’re never home though.

name: Player
dialogue: Oh I see. Do you have any siblings?

name: LI1
dialogue: Nope. Just me in this big, lonely house.

name: Player
dialogue: (It looks like they like to read.)

name: Player
dialogue: Your room is so meticulously clean.

name: LI1
dialogue: Thanks haha. I just like to be organized.

name: Player
dialogue: You’re way neater than me at least. My room is full of random things.

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Ah you know. Books, comics, manga.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: I have a lot of sports equipment laying around.

name: Choice 3
dialogue: A lot of musical instruments haha.

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Ah you know. Books, comics, manga.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: I have a lot of sports equipment laying around.

name: Player
dialogue: Soccer! I've been playing for ten years.

name: Player
dialogue: Ballet. It's my favorite thing to do.

name: Choice 3
dialogue: A lot of musical instruments haha.

name: Player
dialogue: Yup. I love playing classical music.

name: Player
dialogue: Yeah I do a lot of musical covers.

name: LI1
dialogue: That’s so cool, what’s it like? I want to know more about you. *21 questions game*

name: Player
dialogue: We’ve been playing for a while. Should we finally start the project now?

name: LI1
dialogue: Bwahaha yeah. Let’s get to work.

name: Player
dialogue: Me too. We can finish another day.

name: LI1
dialogue: Alright. Are you hungry? I can make dinner.

name: LI1
dialogue: Anything you want! I’m a hella good chef.

name: Player
dialogue: OKAY then, make me your best dish.

name: Player
dialogue: Haha, this is great! How can I thank you? I feel like you’ve been so nice to me.

name: LI1
dialogue: Don’t worry about it. I want to treat you.

name: LI1
dialogue: Wanna work on the project today after school? You can come over again if you’d like.

name: Player
dialogue: We’re almost done with our project.

name: LI1
dialogue: Thank god, this thing is taking so long.

name: Player
dialogue: I don’t think it’s that bad!

name: Choice 1
dialogue: I mean, at least I got to meet you.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: I mean, at least you got ot meet me.

name: LI1
dialogue: Well, we are done with our work.

name: LI1
dialogue: It was nice working with you.

name: Player
dialogue: Same here. Think we can cop a 100?

name: LI1
dialogue: Yes. If not you can seduce the teacher with your pretty face.

name: Player
dialogue: I should get going now. It is pretty late.

name: Player
dialogue: You sure? I don’t want to disrupt.

name: LI1
dialogue: No, don’t worry. You aren’t interrupting anything.

name: Player
dialogue: Wow. Thank you for the meal!

name: Player
dialogue: Ahh, I’m stuffed. I really should get going before my parents start to worry.

name: LI1
dialogue: Yeah of course! Where do you live? I’ll take you home.

name: Player
dialogue: Oh I don’t live too far. About 10 blocks from here?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Awh, you don’t have to. I’ll be fine.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Are you sure? It might be dangerous for you coming back.

name: LI1
dialogue: So tell me more about yourself.

name: Player
dialogue: Hm. Well. I am an only child. I live with my mom and my grandparents. My dad works overseas in Japan.

name: LI1
dialogue: Damn. Japan?? That’s so far. What does he do?

name: Player
dialogue: He’s a businessman! But he should be back soon. My mom is a teacher at an elementary school.

name: Player
dialogue: Hm. Well I want to be an engineer when I grow up.

name: Player
dialogue: Mechanical engineering probably. I just think it’s really interesting.

name: LI1
dialogue: Ah. I’m not too sure yet. There isn’t really much I want to pursue.

name: Player
dialogue: Oh okay, well you still have time.

name: Player
dialogue: Oh we’re here. Thanks for walking me.

name: LI1
dialogue: Of course! Oh, and also… can I ask you something?

name: LI1
dialogue: I was wondering… if you’d like to go out with me sometime?

name: LI1
dialogue: Really?? That makes me so happy. I’m glad. Well, I’ll talk to you later. See you tomorrow.

name: LI1
dialogue: Wanna get food with me after school? My treat.

name: Player
dialogue: Sure. Where do you want to eat?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Kinda craving Japanese food right now.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: I really want to eat Chinese food!

name: LI1
dialogue: That sounds great! I’ll meet with you later.

name: Player
dialogue: Ahhh I should get to class.

name: Player
dialogue: Why is everyone looking at me…?

name: NPC 1
dialogue: I heard you were going out with LI1. Is that true?

name: Chioce 2
dialogue: Why does it matter to you?

name: NPC 1
dialogue: Jeez, no need to get defensive.

name: NPC 1
dialogue: I’m just warning you though. Old classmates say they’re weird.

name: Player
dialogue: Issues..? What are you talking about?

name: NPC 1
dialogue: Don’t worry about it! I’m happy for you guys. Hope you don’t break up soon.

name: LI1
dialogue: It was great! My classes were pretty light and I got to see you. How was yours?'

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Tell them what people are saying.
